    "en": {
      "title": "Interim Budget today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President and Finance Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe will present the Interim Budget in Parliament today.",
        "The President will present this Interim Budget to the Parliament at 1 pm, which has allocated 4672 billion rupees.",
        "After this, the Finance Minister's budget speech will be held till 2 pm.",
        "After that, the House will be adjourned till tomorrow (31st) and the discussion on the second reading of the Interim Budget will be held from tomorrow till the next 2nd.",
        "The poll in this regard is scheduled to be held on the afternoon of the 2nd. (a)"
      ],
